HexLight main firmware
Supported chips:
    PIC32MX2xx family
    Note: PIC32MX1xx family does not support USB
    Note: PIC32MX210F016B does not have enough flash memory for the application!!! Use at least a PIC32MX220F032B or higher

Configurations:
    HexLight_Standalone - For running without a bootloader
    HexLight            - For running with the AN1388 USB bootloader